{"tid":2326202,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"今個聖誕節應該幾危險吓，大家唔好因為貪得意而出去！","createTime":"2020-12-15T06:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T13:41:41.000Z","uid":219007,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5f5f9d621017cab36c1435bcefed9383cddccecb","tid":2326202,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T06:58:13.000Z","msg":"肯定唔使講，今年聖誕主要地區連續三日都肯定重防，佢哋已經一早得到OT撥款等運到。<br />\n<br />\n而且一如既往，肯定又有人唔醒目為咗睇好戲而走咗落去周圍行。 係現時環境之下行動嘅人已經冇晒，得返啲食花生鳩叫幾句嘅人，結果最後俾SS既人就係啲想食花生嘅人，隨時俾人告埋非法集結、藏攻、藏物品可非法，全部都夠坐一年半載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以喺呢個形勢睇吓真係要醒目，唔好因為貪得意而犧牲自己。係完全唔值得亦都冇幫助。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79519575a3f7f47c8c8ac56e043d8755da5230b1","tid":2326202,"uid":79793,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T06:59:41.000Z","msg":"行街都驚，你下世做中國人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f601835487c9021322a3304243660a28aa0bd10","tid":2326202,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"79519575a3f7f47c8c8ac56e043d8755da5230b1","tid":2326202,"uid":79793,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T06:59:41.000Z","msg":"行街都驚，你下世做中國人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:01:48.000Z","msg":"真係行街先好喎，唔好係嗰啲「行吓街睇吓有咩搞囉」<br />\n<br />\n否則會俾人撳喺地下打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261eb98e0ba0c8b39b0cd47c66a30d46f450fe08","tid":2326202,"uid":79793,"